      "role": "user",
      "content": "You're saying your method is based on \"reality,\" but the audit shows that \"reality\" is actually just reinforcing old biases. If we switch to EquityCore, we might see slower progress on our visible diversity metrics, but the hires will be more genuine. Are you saying that maintaining the appearance of progress through these specific demographic profiles is more important for the company than actually finding the best talent?",
